            <div><strong>Forward arm reach in standing erect posture</strong></div>
            <ul type="disc">
                <li>Users are expected to get the feel of the measuring      process through this animated experiment and are advised to measure in      real life practical situations using anthropometric rod sets and      anthropometric boards. Moreover, the users may select their own specific      landmarks as required.</li>
                <li>To refer measurements in other postures i.e. front      bending forward and with one step forward, and the reach values in      sidewise and backward postures the user can go to reference datasheets</li>
            </ul>
